<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-22120] camel-http component is not working with 4.11.0</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-22120</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following code not working when upgrade from 4.6.0 to 4.11.0&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#7f0055&quot;&gt;private&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#7f0055&quot;&gt;static&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#7f0055&quot;&gt;final&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; String &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000c0&quot;&gt;HTTP_DUMMY_HOST&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; = &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#2a00ff&quot;&gt;&quot;http://dummy-host?throwExceptionOnFailure=false&amp;amp;httpClient.connectTimeout=&lt;tt&gt;hobs.crms.connectTimeout&lt;/tt&gt;&amp;amp;httpClient.responseTimeout=&lt;tt&gt;hobs.crms.responseTimeout&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;from(&quot;direct:xtest&quot;)&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; .setHeader(Exchange.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000c0&quot;&gt;CONTENT_TYPE&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;, constant(MediaType.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000c0&quot;&gt;APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;))&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; .setHeader(Exchange.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000c0&quot;&gt;HTTP_METHOD&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;).simple(&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#2a00ff&quot;&gt;&quot;${exchangeProperty.httpmethod}&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; .setHeader(Exchange.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000c0&quot;&gt;HTTP_URI&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;, constant(&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#2a00ff&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;tt&gt;targetsystem.connections.hobs.schema&lt;/tt&gt;://&lt;tt&gt;targetsystem.connections.hobs.host&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;))&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; .setHeader(Exchange.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000c0&quot;&gt;HTTP_PATH&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;).simple(&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#2a00ff&quot;&gt;&quot;${exchangeProperty.path}&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; .choice()&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; .when(simple(&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#2a00ff&quot;&gt;&quot;${exchangeProperty.query} == null&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;))&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; .setHeader(Exchange.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000c0&quot;&gt;HTTP_QUERY&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;, constant(&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#2a00ff&quot;&gt;&quot;bridgeEndpoint=true&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;))&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; .otherwise()&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; .setHeader(Exchange.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0000c0&quot;&gt;HTTP_QUERY&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;).simple(&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#2a00ff&quot;&gt;&quot;${exchangeProperty.query}&amp;amp;bridgeEndpoint=true&quot;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; .end()&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; .to(&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#6a3e3e&quot;&gt;httpHost&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt; .end();&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#000000&quot;&gt;when pass any query parameters then it is failing.&#160; Is HTTP_QUERY not working?&#160;&#160;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
